This Scripts are porwering our Fordpad (kind of a picture Frame) @CCCMZ in Wiesbaden
Feel Free to Use, Share & Modify

ATM these Scripts are a Work in Progress I can't guarantee that everything is working.
(Some files are modifyed without testing or they are missing)
Copy all Files to your root Directory Files gonna be in the right Place, and edit 
your favorite Webserver Config to allow the CGI Scripts located at /usr/local/pad/cgi-bin/
